quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,123,"O ye who believe! fight those who are near to you of the misbelievers, and let them find in you sternness; and know that God is with those who fear"
  9,124,"And whenever a surah is sent down, there are some of them who say, 'Which of you has this increased in faith?' But as for those who believe, it does increase them in faith, and they shall rejoice"
  9,125,"but as for those in whose hearts is sickness, it only adds a plague to their plague, and they die misbelievers"
  9,126,"Do they not see that they are tried in every year once or twice? Yet they do not turn again, nor do they mind"
  9,127,"And whenever a surah is sent down, some of them look at the others - 'Does any one see you?' - Then they turn away! God has turned their hearts, for that they are a people who do not discern"
  9,128,"There has come to you an apostle from amongst yourselves; hard for him to bear is it that ye commit iniquity; he is anxious over you after the believers, pitiful, compassionate"
  9,129,"But if they turn their backs, then say, 'God is enough for me! there is no god but He! upon Him do I rely, for He is Lord of the mighty throne"